Total Vacancies:385

Name of the post:

Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier 

 

Description:

The Rajasthan Cooperative Recruitment Board issued a total of 385 vacancies for the posts of Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier. The online application for the posts of Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier under Rajasthan Cooperative Recruitment Board shall start from 20-03-2021. The eligible candidates can apply for the online application before 20-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, for Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier mentioned below.

. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The interested candidates after filling the application form, it is required to pay the application fee to complete the form submission process:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the General/ BC/ MBC & SC/ST/BC/MBC/ EWS is INR 1200/-
  • The application fee for Sahariya/SC/ST/Non-Creamy layer BC/EWS and MBC/TSP Area/Disabled Candidates of Rajasthan is INR 600/-
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 20-03-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 30-04-2021
  • Last Date for Editing Application Details: 30-04-2021
  • Last Date for Printing Your Application: 15-05-2021

Educational qualification required:

Candidates who are interested in Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier should have the following qualification from a recognized University/boards :

  • You must have a degree in any field to apply for the post of Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier 

Age limit criteria:

The interested candidates must have fallen in the age limit criteria provided by the Rajasthan Cooperative Recruitment Board  is:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 21 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of clerk/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

How to apply for Rajasthan Cooperative Board Various Vacancy Online Form 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Rajasthan Cooperative Recruitment Board.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Clerck/ Junior Assistant/ Salesman/ Godown Keeper/ Store Keeper/ Typist/ Cashier .
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
